<section class="mountain">
  <div class="top-content">
    <img
      src="/assets/photos/Mountain.jpg"
      alt="Sierra Nevada"
      class="mountain-bg"
    />
    <div class="overlay">
      <h2>Over 30 Years of servicing in Shingle Springs.</h2>
      <div class="info-columns">
        <p>
          The Toy Shop have ASE Certified technicians that are able to perform
          any repair from a basic oil change service to engine/<wbr
          />transmission repair or replacement.
          <br /><br />
          We only use factory made parts for the vehicles we service so that you
          know you are getting a quality part for half the price that the dealerships
          charges you.
          <br /><br />
          We scan check engine lights and in most cases basic inspections are at
          no cost. You can call or email the shop and we will get you a fair price
          and quick turnaround time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom-content">
    <h3>Need a second opinion on repairs?</h3>
    <p>
      The Toy Shop offers free honest inspections on any import vehicles to save
      you money!
    </p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <button
        class="button"
        type="button"
        onclick="onShowBooking('d4156edb-ca3a-4e73-bd01-c60ba4bd8e94')"
        >BOOK AN APPOINTMENT</button
      >
      <button
        class="button secondary"
        onclick="window.location.href='tel:+15305551234'">CALL US</button
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  * {
    margin: 0;
  }
  .mountain {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .top-content {
    position: relative;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .mountain-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .overlay {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 4rem 3rem clamp(300px, 10vw, 500px) 3rem;
  }

  .overlay h2 {
    font-family: "apotek-extrawide", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 90%;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .overlay p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: clamp(1.8rem, 2.5vw, 2.2rem);
  }

  .info-columns {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 180%;
    column-count: 3;
    column-gap: 4rem;
    text-align: left;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .info-columns {
      column-count: 2;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .info-columns {
      column-count: 1;
    }
    .overlay h2 {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  /* Bottom */

  .bottom-content {
    background-color: #24222c;
    padding: 2rem 2rem;
  }

  .bottom-content h3 {
    font-family: "apotek-extrawide", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 90%;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .bottom-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 140%;
    color: #fdf499;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .btn-group {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .button {
    background: #f0503a;
    border: 1px solid #fff;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .button.secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid #fff;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .button.secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }
</style>
